Package libshapedraw.event

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LSDEventListener
    Handle events generated by a LibShapeDraw API instance.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LSDEvent
    Abstract base class for all LibShapeDraw events.
    LSDGameTickEvent
    Event fired once per game tick, occurring every 1/20th of a second.
    LSDPreRenderEvent
    Event fired immediately before the API instance's shape collection is rendered.
    LSDRespawnEvent
    Event fired when the player respawns into a new world instance.
